linhello (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging: daemon, PAM module, systemd unit, sysusers group.
    Reseal trigger (kernel postinst.d) installed via `linhello reseal-hook
    install` in postinst. Face login wired via `linhello pam enable`.

